            <h2 class="page-title">How to Care for Your Dog</h2>
            
            <div class="care-content">
                <p>Here are some essential tips for taking care of your dog:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Nutrition:</strong> Provide a balanced diet with appropriate portions of high-quality dog food and ensure fresh water is always available.</li>
                    <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Regular physical activity is crucial for your dog's mental and physical wellbeing. Daily walks and playtime in a safe, enclosed area keep them fit and happy.</li>
                    <li><strong>Comfortable Living Space:</strong> Create a comfortable and clean resting area with a proper dog bed that suits their age and size.</li>
                    <li><strong>Veterinary Care:</strong> Schedule regular check-ups, stay current with vaccinations, stay ontop of their health.</li>
                    <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Use a regular maintenance routine including brushing their coat, bathing when necessary, and trimming their nails.</li>
                </ul>
                
